@NODE About "FM About"

W H A T   I S   T H I S   P R O G R A M   A B O U T 
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

FastMorpher is a realtime morpher. It takes an IFF picture and distorts it
with weird, laughable and sometimes useful results.

The result can be saved in IFF and Anim5 format and is perfect for:
-web publishing
-computer presentations
-video productions

Some people say this process is actually called 'warping', but I will call
it morphing anyway.

@ENDNODE


