@NODE System "FM System Requirements"

S Y S T E M   R E Q U I R E M E N T S
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Minimum requirements:

- an 020 processor
- Amiga DOS 2.04

The AGA chipset is automatically detected and utilized


@ENDNODE


@NODE Install "FM Installing"

I N S T A L L I N G 
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

To install FastMorpher simply drag it's icon to the desired place onto
your harddisk. 

After registering you recieve your own personal keyfile. You can
place this keyfile in the 'S:' or 'FastMorpher' directory.


@ENDNODE


@NODE HowToMorph "FM How To Make A Simple Morph"

H O W   T O   M A K E   A   M O R P H
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

1) Load an IFF picture with the menu item 'project/load IFF...'
2) Distort the picture by dragging the knots by moving the mouse with the 
   left button pressed
3) Select the menu item 'project/store as second key'
4) Select the menu item 'project/play animation'

@ENDNODE


