@NODE Menus "FM Menu Functions"

M E N U   F U N C T I O N S
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

@{" Project " link PMenu} @{" Lattice " link LMenu} @{" Settings " link SMenu}


@ENDNODE


@NODE PMenu "FM Project Menu"

P R O J E C T   M E N U 
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Load IFF...
-----------
Loads an IFF picture from disk.


Save IFF...
-----------
Saves the current picture to disk in the IFF format.


Store as first key
------------------
Stores the current picture as the first key


Store as second key
-------------------
Stores the current picture as the second key


Play animation
--------------
Makes an animation by tweening the first and last key as defined by the 
two above menu items


Save Anim5...
-------------
Saves the animation in the Anim5 format


Set Frames...
-------------
Sets the number of frames


Set Delay time...
-----------------
This is the time between two successive frames in 1/50 seconds


User/Print Registration Form
----------------------------
Prints out the registration form for you.


User/Create RAM:Register.txt
----------------------------
Creates the file ram:register.doc. You can use a text editor to read it's
contents.


User/Make Keyfile...
--------------------
When registering you will recieve your own personal code. Use this menu
item to create your own keyfile.


About...
--------
Information about the program


Quit
----
Any ideas?


@ENDNODE

@NODE LMenu "FM Lattice Menu"

L A T T I C E   M E N U 
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Reset
-----
Resets the lattices


First key
---------
Draws the first key


Last key
--------
Draws the second key


Set Lattice Freq...
-------------------
This is the number knots per horizontal and vertical line


@ENDNODE


@NODE SMenu "FM Settings Menu"

S E T T I N G S    M E N U
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Set Font...
-----------
Loads a font from disk


DblPAL
------
Turns the screen into the DblPAL mode. This will only work if your monitor
supports this screenmode


Load Locale...
--------------
Loads a language from disk


Use internal English
--------------------
Uses the internal English version


@ENDNODE


@NODE Keys "FM Keyboard Functions"

K E Y B O A R D   F U N C T I O N S
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

<tab>		shows the picture without the lattice

<spacebar>	resets the knots

<return>	saves the current picture as the second key and immediately
		starts the animation

+,-		blows up the picture from the current mouse position

r		sets radius of blow

@ENDNODE


